data.description: REDUCED! (WALKING DISTANCE TO DOWNTOWN FLORCENCE!) Beautiful Hill Country ~15 acre property just walking distance to downtown Florence, minutes to IH-35!!! LOCATION!!! There is an attached "proposed survey" for the property for cutting a 10 acre parcel from the total 14.99 acre . 4/2/2 mobile home (in need of full remodel - however, "bones" are good) will convey (or owner will remove from property if buyer prefers) with this land - above ground pool and outbuildings convey as well. The 4.99 acres in the back with the mobile home has a (great) producing Water Well. The 10 acres of land (of the ~15) can be subdivided to produce two 5 acre lots. Each 5 acre parcel is allowed a home PLUS a 2nd (guest) home - so there is a 6 home potential for this property - which could equal INCOME PRODUCING.  Ask Listing Agent for full details on how this property may be purchased/subdivided.
